# Business Model

## Overview

Survonomics is building an integrated software ecosystem for the construction industry. Our business model combines Software-as-a-Service (SaaS), FinTech, marketplace transactions, and premium data services to create multiple recurring revenue streams.

Rather than relying on a single source of income, each product within the Survonomics ecosystem contributes to sustainable long-term revenue while reinforcing the value of the others.

---

# Revenue Streams

## 1. Premium Subscriptions

Construction professionals and businesses can upgrade to premium plans that unlock advanced features.

Premium features include:

- Unlimited project workspaces
- Larger file storage
- Advanced AI tools
- Team management
- Analytics dashboard
- Priority customer support

---

## 2. Enterprise Plans

Construction companies can subscribe to enterprise solutions offering:

- Organization management
- Employee administration
- Advanced permissions
- Compliance tools
- Reporting dashboards
- Dedicated customer support

Enterprise subscriptions provide predictable recurring revenue.

---

## 3. Payment Processing (SurvPay)

SurvPay generates revenue by facilitating secure financial transactions.

Revenue sources include:

- Payment processing fees
- Escrow service fees
- Milestone payment fees
- Merchant services
- Cross-border transaction fees (future)

---

## 4. Marketplace Commission (SurvMarket)

SurvMarket earns revenue by connecting buyers and suppliers.

Revenue sources include:

- Sales commissions
- Premium supplier listings
- Featured product placements
- Advertising opportunities

---

## 5. Data & Price Intelligence (SurvPrice)

Construction professionals depend on accurate pricing information.

Revenue opportunities include:

- Premium price reports
- Market intelligence subscriptions
- Historical pricing data
- Cost forecasting tools
- API access for enterprise customers

---

## 6. Artificial Intelligence Services

AI-powered features will be available through premium plans.

Examples include:

- Cost estimation
- Document summarization
- Procurement recommendations
- Project insights
- Smart search

---

